HOUSTON, United States of America, May 6, 2019/APO Group/ --
                                                        
                            National Energy Services Reunited Corp. (''NESR'' or the ''Company'') (NASDAQ: NESR) (NASDAQ: NESRW) (www.NESR.com), a national, industry-leading provider of integrated energy services in the Middle East and North Africa (''MENA'') and Asia Pacific regions, today announced that it will release its financial results for the first quarter of 2019 on Monday, May 13, 2019. A conference call is scheduled for 10:00 AM ET on May 13, 2019 to discuss such financial results.



Investors, analysts and members of the media interested in listening to the conference call are encouraged to participate by dialing in to the U.S. toll-free line at 1-877-407-0312 or the international line at 1-201-389-0899. A live, listen-only webcast will also be available under the ''Investors'' section of the Company's website atÂ www.NESR.com. A replay of the conference call will be available after the event under the ''Investors'' section of the Company's website.